dr.app.beast
Class BeastVersion

java.lang.Object
  dr.app.beast.BeastVersion
All Implemented Interfaces:
Version
public class BeastVersion
extends java.lang.Object
implements Version

This class provides a mechanism for returning the version number of the dr software. It relies on the administrator of the dr source using the module tagging system in CVS. The method getVersionString() will return the version of dr under the following condition:
1. the dr source has been checked out *by tag* before being packaged for distribution.

Author:
Alexei Drummond, Andrew Rambaut
